<paragraph id="8BEF36A3FFF8FFD9A5F8FF3F1A71FEAD" blockId="8.[136,1452,158,401]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFF8FFD9A5F8FF3F1F19FEC0" bold="true" box="[189,294,230,256]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Notes:—</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFF8FFD9A463FF3F1FC6FEC0" authorityName="Troncoso" authorityYear="1962" baseAuthorityName="Gillies &amp; Hooker ex Hooker" box="[294,505,230,256]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Aloysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="gratissima">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFF8FFD9A463FF3F1FC6FEC0" box="[294,505,230,256]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">Aloysia gratissima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is recognized by the leaves with entire margin, conspicuous main vein, prominent only in the abaxial surface, and solitary axillary racemes. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC14B52FFF8FFD9A7B8FED31DE3FEE5" author="Moroni, P. &amp; O'Leary, N. &amp; Filloy, J." box="[765,988,266,293]" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" pagination="193 - 212" refId="ref36202" refString="Moroni, P., O'Leary, N. &amp; Filloy, J. (2016) Species delimitation in the Aloysia gratissima complex (Verbenaceae) following the phylogenetic species concept. Botanical journal of the Linnean Society 180: 193 - 212. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / boj. 12369" type="journal article" year="2016">
Moroni 
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFF8FFD9A613FED21DB2FEE4" box="[854,909,266,292]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">et al.</emphasis>
(2016)
</bibRefCitation>
consider two varieties for this species: the type-variety with smaller leaves (5.3–)9.9–19(–28.3) × (2–)3.6–7.3(–11) mm and 
<taxonomicName id="4C504D20FFF8FFD9A15EFEF61F7EFEAD" authority="(Briquet) Botta (1979: 85)" authorityName="Botta" authorityPageNumber="85" authorityYear="1979" baseAuthorityName="Briquet" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" genus="Aloysia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="variety" species="gratissima" variety="sellowii">
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFF8FFD9A15EFEF61A8FFE88" box="[1051,1200,303,329]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">A. gratissima</emphasis>
var. 
<emphasis id="B924EAB1FFF8FFD9A1A2FEF71B01FE88" box="[1255,1342,302,328]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">sellowii</emphasis>
(Briquet) Botta (1979: 85)
</taxonomicName>
with larger leaves (17.7–)20.7–32.4(–38.7) × (5.7–)7.7–13(–16) mm.
</paragraph>
